          "description": "I can\u2019t say enough good things about this medical urgent care center. The staff are pleasantly professional and caring! I went in with a with an urgent problem and within minutes the procedure recommended took less than 5 minutes and I felt so good to relieved and happy my pain was gone the relief was instant and problem that was causing the pain was manually eliminated. Heather you are an Angel \u2764\ufe0f People sleep sound and so grateful for your God Given Medical Dr. Profession! Prayers be with you all at your wonderful clean warm practice \ud83d\ude4f",
