          "description": "Avoid this place. They charged me copay for my annual flu shot even though my insurance confirmed full coverage. The scrawny Hispanic woman at the front desk was beyond rude and unhelpful. When I called their other location, they confirmed there was no copay for the flu shot. There was also no notices of the extra charge. Businesses don\u2019t understand how important it is to have good customer interfacing staff. They are your first line of sale. When they suck, no will bother moving forward. Really shady.",
